<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{% block title %}ForumInfinite - BAN HAMMER{% endblock %}</title>

    {# Import Tailwind CSS #}
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    {# Import Font Awesome for Icons #}
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center">

{% block body %}
    <div class="bg-red-700 border-4 border-red-900 text-center rounded-lg p-8 max-w-2xl shadow-2xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold uppercase text-white mb-4 tracking-widest animate-pulse">
            <i class="fas fa-gavel mr-2"></i>Ban Hammer Activated!
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-white font-semibold bg-red-800 p-4 rounded shadow-inner">
            Votre compte a été banni. Si vous pensez qu'il s'agit d'une erreur, veuillez contacter l'administrateur.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-yellow-300">
            Cause du bannissement : A dit <span class="text-yellow-500">Laravel > Symfony</span>.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6">
            <a href="/logout" class="bg-yellow-500 hover:bg-yellow-400 text-black font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded shadow">
                Contacter l'administrateur
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
</body>
</html>
